subSubSection.paragraph:
Male genitalia
(
Figs 5, 6
) (genital preparation No. 0 47 NY, 2017). Tegumen -uncus complex (
Fig. 5
) broad with individual setae apically; scopula androconialis undeveloped; gnathos with crista gnathi lateralis large and ovoid, crista gnathi medialis shorter and more narrow; valva trapeziform, crista sacculi short with strong bifurcate setae, crista centralis long and broad; aedeagus (
Fig. 6
) narrow, about 1.5 times as long as valva; vesica with two small cornuti.
